[The public health world is watching Italy to see if they are successful in implementing these new rules, and to see if the implementation of these rules will have an impact on disease transmission. I suspect many of the European countries are weighing the pros and cons of implementing similar measures.

The Chinese appeared to have successfully slowed transmission of the SARS-CoV-2. Is it feasible and will it work outside of China? - Mod.MPP]

